<chapter>
  <title><xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_Received_LOI"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" /> Module</title>

  <para role="TEXT">The <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_Received_LOI"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" /> module enables you, on behalf
  of your company (the beneficiary) to receive notification of Letters of
  Indemnity, and subsequent updates, from the Issuing Bank. You can also send
  messages back to the bank for events that require your approval or
  acceptance in the ongoing transaction flow.</para>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>Functions</title>

    <para role="TEXT">The menu for this module has the following groups of functions. All
    are basically as described in the chapter
    <emphasis>Functions</emphasis>.</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Message to
        Bank</guimenuitem></term>

        <listitem>
          <para role="TEXT">Send a free-format message to the Issuing Bank regarding a
          Received Letter of Indemnity that the bank has notified you
          of.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para role="TEXT">The <emphasis role="bold">Pending RIs</emphasis>, <emphasis
    role="bold">RI Inquiry</emphasis>, and <emphasis role="bold">RI
    Maintenance</emphasis> parts of the menu are as described in chapter
    <emphasis>Functions</emphasis>.</para>
  </section>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>Message to Bank</title>

    <para role="TEXT">This section describes the <guimenuitem>Message to
    Bank</guimenuitem> part of the menu and the forms it uses.</para>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Message to Bank Functions</title>

      <para role="TEXT">This part of the menu contains several functions, providing
      different ways to send a free-format message to the Issuing Bank.</para>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>From Existing RI</title>

        <para role="TEXT">As described in chapter <emphasis>Functions</emphasis>, except
        that this function displays a list of existing Received Letters of
        Indemnity, that is, Letters of Indemnity that your company (the
        beneficiary) has received notification of from the Issuing
        Bank.</para>
      </section>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>Retrieve Draft</title>

        <para role="TEXT">As described in chapter <emphasis>Functions</emphasis>.</para>
      </section>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>Retrieve Unsigned</title>

        <para role="TEXT">As described in chapter <emphasis>Functions</emphasis>.</para>
      </section>
    </section>

    <section condition="TITLE=Received Letter of Indemnity - Free Format Message;PERM=ri_access;ACCESS=RI_02"
             role="TOPIC">
      <title>Message to Bank Form</title>

      <para role="TEXT">The input form for you to enter the details of the free-format
      message is as follows:</para>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>General Details</title>

        <informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="3">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="3.0*" />

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1.0*" />

            <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="5.0*" />

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Type</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel moreinfo="none">Full
                Transaction Details</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_action.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ACTION" width="3mm" />
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">(Button at the right-hand side of
                the General Details title line.) Open a popup window to show
                the full details of the current Received Letter of
                Indemnity.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel moreinfo="none">System
                Id</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_info.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_INFO" width="4mm" />
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Unique reference number that was
                generated by <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml"
                xpointer="ent_appli"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" /> for this Letter
                of Indemnity when the bank created it.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel moreinfo="none">Bank
                Reference</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_info.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_INFO" width="4mm" />
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Reference assigned by the bank's
                back office to this Letter of Indemnity when the bank created
                it.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
      </section>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>Free Format Message</title>

        <informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="3">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="3.0*" />

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1.0*" />

            <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="5.0*" />

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Type</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel moreinfo="none">Free
                Format Message</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Text of your message to the
                bank.</para><para role="TEXT">Up to 100 lines of 65 characters
                each.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
      </section>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>File Upload Details</title>

        <informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="3">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="3.0*" />

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1.0*" />

            <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="6.0*" />

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Type</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel moreinfo="none">File
                Upload Details</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_action.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ACTION" width="3mm" />
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Optionally, a list of files from
                your local hard disk giving additional details pertaining to
                this Letter Of Indemnity. Click <guibutton>Add a
                file</guibutton> to add a file.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
      </section>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>Inquiry and Maintenance</title>

    <para role="TEXT">The <emphasis role="bold">Pending RIs</emphasis>, <emphasis
    role="bold">RI Inquiry</emphasis>, and <emphasis role="bold">RI
    Maintenance</emphasis> parts of the menu are as described in chapter
    <emphasis>Functions</emphasis>.</para>
  </section>
</chapter>
